    {
      "messages": [
        {
          "content": "Get ready for the Beneficial AGI Challenge! Over the next day, you'll delve into the potential of AGI in the tech industry and its ethical considerations. Stay tuned for the first set of tasks.",
          "time": "08:00:00"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "messages": [
        {
          "content": "The Beneficial AGI Challenge begins today! Prepare to explore the intersection of AGI and the tech industry, and discover how it can be harnessed for positive impact. The first tasks will be revealed soon.",
